{"tid":1179681,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有關PlayStationPlus訂閱價格的重要通知","createTime":"2019-05-31T09:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T21:47:54.000Z","uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"096bcc6b225d53a239a5d7262a58120174e23983","tid":1179681,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"從 2019年8月1日起, 香港地區的PlayStation Plus會籍訂閱價格將會改訂，詳情如下:<br />\nPlayStation Plus 12個月會籍訂閱價格將變更為 HK$308<br />\nPlayStation Plus 3個月會籍訂閱價格將變更為 HK$128<br />\nPlayStation Plus 1個月會籍訂閱價格將變更為 HK$48<br />\n改訂價格將於2019年8月1日起實施。<br />\n於當天或之後支付的任何訂閱款項將以改訂後的訂閱價格收費。<br />\n<br />\n價格改訂對您的影響:<br />\n<br />\n我們將在2019年8月1日改訂PlayStation Plus會籍的收費。由於您是既有會員，所有於2019年8月1日後的續訂將以改訂後價格收費。2019年8月1日之前您依然可以原定價格訂閱 PlayStation Plus會籍，添加或累計至您原有的會籍之中。 <br />\n<br />\n若您不希望繼續訂閱，請務必於2019年8月1日以前關閉自動訂閱功能，以取消訂閱。"},{"pid":"bdae234fd3782df38f23b67fa45133eb82cafbd9","tid":1179681,"uid":251665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"唔知8月前會唔會有優惠"},{"pid":"ae998a96f1c00b7c66df2b9af3806d310f5c639d","tid":1179681,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"之前係咪268一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f663b753e4ed662e7849f5f51c6efb90a07f58","tid":1179681,"uid":32455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdae234fd3782df38f23b67fa45133eb82cafbd9","tid":1179681,"uid":251665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"唔知8月前會唔會有優惠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"Days of Play有7折 6月7開始<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以一次買兩年⋯"},{"pid":"83b962018991ea8892c671e1b3875ee783212a93","tid":1179681,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae998a96f1c00b7c66df2b9af3806d310f5c639d","tid":1179681,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"之前係咪268一年<img src=\"/assets/faces